Students meet regularly to report on the progress of their MA thesis or project, to share experiences, and to give and receive written and oral feedback on their work; oral presentation at the MA school's autumn school.Objectives/eesmärkid:  This course aims to support the progress of the MA thesis or MA project by means of developing related skills and providing students with opportunities to give and receive constructive collegial feedback and to share best practices.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon successful completion of this course, students should:
*	have enhanced their ability to plan their work, to stick to time frames and to work both independently and in teams;
*	have improved their oral and written communication skills;
*	have developed their ability to give constructive feedback, to work with feedback on their work and to reflect on their abilities and needs;
*	have broadened their horizons through familiarizing themselves with their colleagues' work.
